{"title":"The Fizik Vento Infinito Carbon 2 Wide Brings Comfort to Road Racing Shoes","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/10/22/the-fizik-vento-infinito-carbon-2-wide-brings-comfort-to-road-racing-shoes/","date":1634925602000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21091722/fizik-infinito-wide-1.jpg\" data-fancybox=\"\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21091722/fizik-infinito-wide-1-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"two fizik infinito wide shoes against a white background\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21091722/fizik-infinito-wide-1-800x534.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21091722/fizik-infinito-wide-1-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21091722/fizik-infinito-wide-1-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21091722/fizik-infinito-wide-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21091722/fizik-infinito-wide-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21091722/fizik-infinito-wide-1.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></a><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-275675\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>Time to give those piggies some breathing room. Fizik is maxing out the comfort with wider, higher-volume additions to its Vento line of road racing shoes. The Vento Infinito Carbon 2 Wide models come in both Microtex and knit uppers, with stiff carbon outsoles and a precise, dialed-in fit. Let’s peep the specs.</p><h2>Vento Infinito Carbon 2 Wide</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21093235/fizik-infinito-wide-2.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21093235/fizik-infinito-wide-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21093235/fizik-infinito-wide-2.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21093235/fizik-infinito-wide-2-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21093235/fizik-infinito-wide-2-800x534.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21093235/fizik-infinito-wide-2-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21093235/fizik-infinito-wide-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21093235/fizik-infinito-wide-2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p><strong>Specs:</strong></p><ul><li>Wide fit shoes</li><li>Microtex upper</li><li>Li2 Dual Zone BOA® Fit System configuration</li><li>R2 outsole – full carbon unidirectional, stiffness index 10</li><li>Weight: 229g (size 42 – 1/2 pair)</li><li>Sizes: 36-48 (37 to 47 also in half sizes)</li><li>Vento: performance racing series designed in collaboration with professional cyclists</li><li>Intended use: road racing</li></ul><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21094354/fizik-infinito-wide-3.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21094354/fizik-infinito-wide-3.jpg\" alt=\"the outsole of the vento infinito carbon 2 wide against a white background\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21094354/fizik-infinito-wide-3.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21094354/fizik-infinito-wide-3-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21094354/fizik-infinito-wide-3-800x534.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21094354/fizik-infinito-wide-3-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21094354/fizik-infinito-wide-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21094354/fizik-infinito-wide-3-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>Things we like here? How about that clean white and black Microtex styling, half-size availability, and carbon outsole? Dig the cleat positioning—it’s set a little further back than is traditional, which is easier on the knees and supports aggressive riding posture.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21095752/fizik-infinito-wide-4.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21095752/fizik-infinito-wide-4.jpg\" alt=\"A close-up of the plantar region of the fizik shoe\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21095752/fizik-infinito-wide-4.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21095752/fizik-infinito-wide-4-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21095752/fizik-infinito-wide-4-800x534.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21095752/fizik-infinito-wide-4-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21095752/fizik-infinito-wide-4-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21095752/fizik-infinito-wide-4-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>But of course, it’s the fit that stands out with these wide models. Fizik utilizes a whole range of design features to achieve maximum comfort. That black area on the upper isn’t just for flash—it’s adjustable and designed to support your plantar fascia.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21100102/fizik-infinito-wide-5.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21100102/fizik-infinito-wide-5.jpg\" alt=\"vento infinito carbon 2 wide shoes against a white background\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21100102/fizik-infinito-wide-5.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21100102/fizik-infinito-wide-5-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21100102/fizik-infinito-wide-5-800x534.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21100102/fizik-infinito-wide-5-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21100102/fizik-infinito-wide-5-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21100102/fizik-infinito-wide-5-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>You can also control the volume of the forefoot and the precise tension of the laces with Fizik’s BOA lacing system. When combined with the wide fit across the metatarsals and the higher volume at the ball of the foot, you end up with a road-racing shoe designed to keep your feet comfortable as the miles unwind behind you. Even better? The shoe also comes in knit.</p><p>Pricing for the Vento Infinito Carbon 2 Wide starts at $359.99, with a Movistar Team edition available for $369.99.</p><h2>The Vento Infinito Knit Carbon 2 Wide</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21101122/fizik-infinito-wide-6.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21101122/fizik-infinito-wide-6.jpg\" alt=\"the Vento Infinito Knit Carbon 2 wide against a white background\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21101122/fizik-infinito-wide-6.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21101122/fizik-infinito-wide-6-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21101122/fizik-infinito-wide-6-800x534.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21101122/fizik-infinito-wide-6-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21101122/fizik-infinito-wide-6-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21101122/fizik-infinito-wide-6-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p><strong>Specs:</strong></p><ul><li>Wide fit shoes</li><li>Knitted upper</li><li>Li2 Dual Zone BOA® Fit System configuration</li><li>R2 outsole – full carbon unidirectional, stiffness index 10</li><li>Weight: 225g (size 42 – 1/2 pair)</li><li>Sizes: 36-48 (37 to 47 also in half sizes)</li><li>Vento: performance racing series designed in collaboration with professional cyclists</li><li>Intended use: road racing</li></ul><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21101647/fizik-infinito-wide-7.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21101647/fizik-infinito-wide-7.jpg\" alt=\"a close up of the vento infinito knit carbon 2 wide's knit material \" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21101647/fizik-infinito-wide-7.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21101647/fizik-infinito-wide-7-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21101647/fizik-infinito-wide-7-800x534.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21101647/fizik-infinito-wide-7-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21101647/fizik-infinito-wide-7-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/21101647/fizik-infinito-wide-7-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>The Vento Infinito Knit Carbon 2 Wide shaves a few grams and ups the breathability for hot and humid road races but maintains the features of the Microtex version. Downside? It’s slightly more expensive at $379.99.</p><p>We recommend checking out Fizik’s sizing guide before making a purchase.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.fizik.com/\">fizik.com</a></p></section></article></div></div>","author":"Andrew Marshall","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"0666d2420e83100802038ada3a012a9a62eba7c1c0affdbf76ce2c376ab79f94","category":"Cycling"}